---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const lang = 'en';
---
<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Harezm Technology" lang={lang}>
    <div class="pt-32 pb-24 bg-surface min-h-screen">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-8 md:px-0">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-headline font-bold text-on-background mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
            <div class="space-y-6 text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed font-light">
                <p>At Harezm Technology, we respect your privacy and enforce strict rules to ensure the confidentiality of data acquired during our business processes.</p>
                
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-on-background mt-10 mb-4">Our Data Security Standards</h2>
                <p>Corporate communication information, trade secrets, or project metrics collected by us are strictly not subject to sale, rental, or distribution to third parties for marketing purposes. All industry-standard security measures are actively implemented on our servers.</p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-on-background mt-10 mb-4">Third-Party Links</h2>
                <p>There may be links to other websites (such as LinkedIn, GitHub, etc.) on our site. Harezm is not responsible for the privacy policies or contents of the linked sites.</p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-on-background mt-10 mb-4">Modifications</h2>
                <p>Harezm reserves the right to modify this privacy policy without prior notice in accordance with technological and legal requirements.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
